- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper presents a new approach to language modeling.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as the SWITCHBOARD corpus used in the experiments is a collection of telephone conversations.
